room_title: Escape room "Mr. Jenkins Basement" by Nut House Escape Rooms in Rochester (NY)
review: I've been to several escape rooms in rochester, N.Y. and this one is by far the best. Loved Mr Jenkins basement. Very challenging and fun. Would highly recommend it with a large group.

room_title: Escape room "Mr. Jenkins Basement" by Nut House Escape Rooms in Rochester (NY)
review: So much fun! We did Mr Jenkins Basement and even though we didn't make it out in time it was well worth it.

room_title: Escape room "Mr. Jenkins Basement" by Nut House Escape Rooms in Rochester (NY)
review: Love the rooms at the Nuthouse! Mr. Jenkins basement was really fun and very challenging. Looking forward to new rooms.
